texts.content: {"text":"إِذَا جَآءَ نَصْرُ ٱللَّهِ وَٱلْفَتْحُ ﴿١﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"وَرَأَيْتَ ٱلنَّاسَ يَدْخُلُونَ فِى دِينِ ٱللَّهِ أَفْوَاجًۭا ﴿٢﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,65]}]}

{"text":"فَسَبِّحْ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّكَ وَٱسْتَغْفِرْهُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ تَوَّابًۢا ﴿٣﴾","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.984313726425171,0.76862746477127075,0.45882353186607361]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":12,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,74]}]}

{"text":"2. Va odamlarning Allohning diniga \nto`p-to`p bo`lib kirayotganini ko`rsang...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,78]}]}

{"text":"3. Bas, Robbingni poklab yod et va Unga istig`for ayt. Albatta, U tavbalarni ko`plab qabul etuvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"range":[0,102]}]}

{"text":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,0.74901962280273438,0.45098039507865906]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":14,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,40]}]}
